          <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">Mistake #2: Vague Services</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">"Tax Services, Accounting" with no detail. No process explanation.</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-red-600 font-black">RESULT: 68% can't tell if you solve their specific problem.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border-l-[3px] border-red-500 p-6 shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">Mistake #3: Hidden Pricing</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">"Contact for quote" instead of transparent service fees.</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-red-600 font-black">RESULT: 54% skip to next CPA with visible pricing.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border-l-[3px] border-red-500 p-6 shadow-md">
