          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">Generalist positioning. No niche expertise visible.</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-red-600 font-black">RESULT: Premium clients with complex situations assume you can't help.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border-l-[3px] border-red-500 p-6 shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">Mistake #5: No Social Proof</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">No testimonials, no client results, no case studies.</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-red-600 font-black">RESULT: 61% question if you actually deliver results.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border-l-[3px] border-red-500 p-6 shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">Mistake #6: Frictionful Contact</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">Form required, no phone, difficult booking process.</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-red-600 font-black">RESULT: 47% abandon to find easier CPA to reach.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- UNEXPECTED FINDINGS -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-[#ECFDF5]">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-emerald-50 border-[3px] border-green-300 p-6 md:p-8 my-10">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">Unexpected Findings After 40 Hours Testing</h2>
