        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-green-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">CPA license visible: 5x more qualified clients</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">CPA buried license number. Added "CPA License #12345, IRS Enrolled Agent" prominently. Month 1: 5x more qualified inquiries. Visible credentials = qualified = trust = hire you.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-green-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Service areas clear: 4x better client fit</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Added "Tax Preparation, Tax Planning, IRS Resolution" prominently. Month 1: 4x more qualified calls. Clear services = you solve my problem = hire you.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-green-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Pricing transparent: 67% more qualified leads</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Added "Tax Prep: $300+" with service guide prominently. Month 1: 67% more qualified inquiries. Price transparency = can afford = hire you.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-green-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Specializations visible: 53% more niche clients</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Added "Crypto Tax Expert, Real Estate Professional" prominently. Month 1: 53% more high-value niche inquiries. Specialization = expert = premium fees = hire you.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-green-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Mobile booking: 73% of taxpayers search on phones</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Tax season = search on phone. Non-responsive booking = they call elsewhere. Mobile-optimized = they book. Tax = mobile urgency.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-green-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Case studies matter: 81% more premium clients</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Added crypto tax savings case study ($47K saved). Month 1: 81% more high-value inquiries. Results = you deliver = I hire you = pay more.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TOOL COMPARISONS -->
