            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-emerald-600 font-black text-xl">‚úì</span><div><p class="font-bold text-gray-900">Custom Credential Layouts</p><p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Design credential pages exactly how CPAs need. License, certifications, IRS status front and center.</p></div></li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-emerald-600 font-black text-xl">‚úì</span><div><p class="font-bold text-gray-900">Service CMS</p><p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Manage services as database entries. Easy to update tax prep, planning, resolution offerings.</p></div></li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-emerald-600 font-black text-xl">‚úì</span><div><p class="font-bold text-gray-900">Professional Design Control</p><p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Full design freedom. Create trust-building layouts that communicate expertise.</p></div></li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-emerald-600 font-black text-xl">‚úì</span><div><p class="font-bold text-gray-900">Fast PageSpeed</p><p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Score 95+. Tax season searches = instant credential verification.</p></div></li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-4">WEBFLOW LIMITATIONS</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-red-600 font-black text-xl">‚úó</span><div><p class="font-bold text-gray-900">Learning Curve</p><p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Takes 2-3 days to learn. Not ideal if you need a site tomorrow.</p></div></li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-red-600 font-black text-xl">‚úó</span><div><p class="font-bold text-gray-900">Requires Setup</p><p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Forms, CMS, hosting need configuration. Not plug-and-play.</p></div></li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-red-600 font-black text-xl">‚úó</span><div><p class="font-bold text-gray-900">No Native Booking</p><p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Need Calendly or similar integration for consultation scheduling.</p></div></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-emerald-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-gray-900 mb-3">BEST FOR CPAs WHO NEED</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Custom credential layouts, exact service control, professional design freedom. If you're a CPA who needs specific credential presentation and want full design control, Webflow delivers. Not ideal if you want instant setup.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DETAILED BREAKDOWN: SQUARESPACE -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-8">Squarespace AI for Tax Professionals: Professional Trust</h2>

      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-50 to-green-50 border-[3px] border-emerald-200 p-8 rounded-lg">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-8">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-4">WHY SQUARESPACE FOR TAX</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-emerald-600 font-black text-xl">‚úì</span><div><p class="font-bold text-gray-900">Finance Templates</p><p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Professional templates designed for financial services. Built-in credential sections.</p></div></li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-emerald-600 font-black text-xl">‚úì</span><div><p class="font-bold text-gray-900">Built-in Credibility</p><p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Testimonial sections, case study layouts, client result displays.</p></div></li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-emerald-600 font-black text-xl">‚úì</span><div><p class="font-bold text-gray-900">Integrated Forms</p><p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Consultation request forms with tax situation fields. Easy client qualification.</p></div></li>
